reviews.review_text:
Been waiting 20 years for this Thanx Greg and mtownshend.  I went the opposite way, SF to FL, for these shows and have not been able to hear it since.  I would strongly recommend a listen before downloading/burning.  The bass sounds awful as alluded to earlier today.  Vocals are a tad in the back.  
I like the vocal jam out of He's Gone and the drums have a unique quality to them.  Hey Jude to close the set is unusual.  The Sun Gonna Shine verse in the Rider is very energetic.  I'm happy to have this since I was there.  
The second set fits easily onto one cd.  Peace
